
1. test class MUST be "public"

2. test method MUST be "public"

3. return type of test method MUST be "void"

4. NO input parameter for test method

5. test method MUST has @Test annotation

6. Each class can have MANY test methods,
   each method can execute independently

7. test one test method: select specific test method
   test ALL test methods: 1. select blank space 2. run Test class

8. DO NOT name a class as "Test" except for testing to avoid naming collision